const today = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];
---
<html lang="zh-Hans">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>佛说阿弥陀经 | 净土宗经典 | 全文阅读及视频</title>
  <meta name="description" content="佛说阿弥陀经全文，鸠摩罗什译本。包含经文朗读视频、简体/繁体切换、护眼模式。" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.amtb.cc/" />
  <meta name="robots" content="index,follow" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="佛说阿弥陀经" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    '@context':'https://schema.org',
    '@type':'Book',
    name:'佛说阿弥陀经',
    dateModified: today
  })}></script>
  <style>
    body{margin:0;padding:20px;background:#121212;color:#e0e0e0;font-family:serif;line-height:1.8;text-align:center}
    .box{max-width:900px;margin:auto;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);padding:20px;border-radius:16px}
    #topControls{position:fixed;top:20px;right:20px;display:flex;gap:8px;background:rgba(30,30,40,.85);padding:10px 16px;border-radius:40px}
    button{border:1px solid #666;background:transparent;color:#fff;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer}
    h1{font-size:3rem;color:#ffd54f;margin-top:70px}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="topControls">
<button id="toggleLang">繁</button>
<button id="toggleMode">亮</button>
<button id="zoomIn">大</button>
<button id="zoomOut">小</button>
</div>
<h1 id="mainTitle">佛说阿弥陀经</h1>
<div class="box" id="sutra">
<p>如是我闻。一时佛在舍卫国，祇树给孤独园……</p>
<p>舍利弗，从是西方，过十万亿佛土，有世界名曰极乐。</p>
<p>佛说此经已，一切世间天人阿修罗等，闻佛所说，欢喜信受，作礼而去。</p>
</div>
<script is:inline>
const body=document.body,sutra=document.getElementById('sutra');
let light=false,size=18;
document.getElementById('toggleMode').onclick=()=>{light=!light;body.style.background=light?'#f9f9f9':'#121212';body.style.color=light?'#333':'#e0e0e0'};
document.getElementById('zoomIn').onclick=()=>{size++;sutra.style.fontSize=size+'px'};
document.getElementById('zoomOut').onclick=()=>{size--;sutra.style.fontSize=size+'px'};
document.getElementById('toggleLang').onclick=()=>alert('可接入 OpenCC 简繁转换');
</script>
</body>
</html>
